{"type": "article", "id": 54972, "title": "迪丽热巴代言哈根达斯，苹果 App Store 有 10 亿用户｜乙方日报", "description": "这里有营销和营销人相关的一切", "date": "2018-07-06T05:46:25Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 29, "name": "Top 15"}, {"id": 393, "name": "收购"}, {"id": 1821, "name": "App Store"}, {"id": 68, "name": "苹果"}, {"id": 1353, "name": "哈根达斯"}, {"id": 18974, "name": "滴滴出行"}, {"id": 1318, "name": "WPP"}], "category": 18, "column": 31, "author": 1375, "comment_count": 7, "praise_count": 16, "image": "img/article/article_show/20180706115731ozEWOIVdXbDljJt6.jpg", "contents": "<h3 finallycleanhtml=\"true\" nocleanhtml=\"true\">明星又代言了啥</h3><p><a href=\"https://m.weibo.cn/status/4257999297901921?wm=3333_2001&amp;from=1086393010&amp;sourcetype=weixin&amp;featurecode=newtitle\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>迪丽热巴代言哈根达斯。</strong></a>同时，哈根达斯宣布将于 7 月 20 日举办上海蜜桃派对，蜜桃派对也是哈根达斯今年夏季新品。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180706111657twUg5Wr8NKOTVjd1.png\" data-ratio=\"0.561250\" data-format=\"png\"> </figure></div><p><strong><a href=\"https://www.prnasia.com/story/216153-1.shtml\" rel=\"nofollow\">黄轩成为威斯汀酒店大中华区代言人，为其拍摄了广告片。</a></strong>黄轩担任威斯汀酒店大中华区全新品牌健康生活大使，推广该品牌酒店对于健康、运动的关注。</p><div class=\"com-insert-embeds\"> <figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/iframe/player.html?vid=g0712c4gyje&amp;tiny=0&amp;auto=0\"></iframe> </figure> </div><h3>值得一提的 Case</h3><p><a href=\"https://www.retaildive.com/news/amazon-unboxing-unforgettable-events-in-prime-day-stunt/527124/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>亚马逊开始预热</strong><strong> Prime Day </strong><strong>会员促销活动，搬来了一个</strong><strong> 7.6 </strong><strong>米长的快递箱。</strong></a>亚马逊在伦敦、东京、米兰、纽约等地放置了标记着公司“微笑脸”标志的大型快递箱，称会带来现场活动。</p><div class=\"com-insert-embeds\"> <figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/iframe/player.html?vid=g0712jlqa42&amp;tiny=0&amp;auto=0\"></iframe> </figure> </div><p><a href=\"http://community.xiaojukeji.com/market/lvwashougongshu01/index.html?ADTAG=map&amp;from=timeline&amp;isappinstalled=0\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>滴滴出行与《旅行青蛙》合作拍摄定格动画。</strong></a>短片引用了不少《旅行青蛙》游戏中的明信片，讲述小青蛙找妈妈的故事，主推的是滴滴出行的行程分享功能。只是滴滴出行现在再找《旅行青蛙》合作晚了不少。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180706113839fd7tL9gVTUDl20jR.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.948405\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><h3>有些数字你可能感兴趣</h3><p><a href=\"https://www.apple.com/cn/newsroom/2018/07/app-store-turns-10/?from=timeline&amp;isappinstalled=0\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>10 </strong><strong>亿</strong></a>——昨天，苹果公司在应用商店 App Store 10 周年之际公布了一些新的数字。2008 年 7 月 10 日上线以来，目前 App Store 的用户超过 10 亿。</p><h3>其他，也挺重要</h3><p><a href=\"http://www.thedrum.com/news/2018/07/05/wpp-threatens-revoke-20m-sorrell-payoff-over-mediamonks-bid\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>WPP </strong><strong>与前</strong><strong> CEO </strong><strong>苏铭天争夺制作公司</strong><strong> MediaMonks</strong><strong>，还威胁称要取消苏铭天</strong><strong> 2000 </strong><strong>万英镑的股票奖励。</strong></a>WPP 通过律师事务所 Slaughter &amp; May 称，苏铭天继续计划收购 MediaMonks 的行为，可能会泄露其离职协议相关内容，WPP 会将取消股票奖励。</p><p><a href=\"https://mashable.com/2018/07/05/facebook-declaration-of-independence-hate-speech/?utm_campaign=Mash-Prod-RSS-Feedburner-All-Partial&amp;utm_cid=Mash-Prod-RSS-Feedburner-All-Partial&amp;utm_source=feedly&amp;utm_medium=webfeeds#YJk3lRPPxkqO\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>错将《美国独立宣言》内容识别为仇恨言论，</strong><strong>Facebook </strong><strong>为此道歉。</strong></a>德州报纸 <em>The Liberty County Vindicator </em>在Facebook上发布《美国独立宣言》部分内容时，被 Facebook 标记为内容涉及仇恨言论。Facebook 后续回复承认出现差错，将内容恢复。</p><p><br></p><p>题图来自：Pexels</p>"}